        If you have any questions about our locations or services, we're here to help.
      </p>
      <a 
        href="/contact" 
        class="inline-block bg-primary-500 hover:bg-primary-600 text-white font-medium px-8 py-3 rounded-md transition transform hover:scale-105"
      >
        Contact Us
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>